{"id": "art-163", "label": "Art. 163", "title": "Art. 163", "slug": "art-163", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 163 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_620362806\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2001\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_620362806\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Cenzorii sunt <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;i</span>\ns&#259; supravegheze gestiunea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\ns&#259; verifice dac&#259; <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span> financiare\nsunt legal întocmite <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în <span class=SpellE>concordan&#355;&#259;</span>\ncu registrele, dac&#259; acestea din urm&#259; sunt <span class=SpellE>&#355;inute</span>\nregulat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> dac&#259; evaluarea elementelor\npatrimoniale s-a f&#259;cut conform regulilor stabilite pentru întocmirea <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> prezentarea <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iilor</span>\nfinanciare.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1226399495\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2000\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1226399495\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Despre toate acestea, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nasupra propunerilor pe care le vor considera necesare cu privire la <span\nclass=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span> financiare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nrepartizarea profitului, cenzorii vor prezenta adun&#259;rii generale un raport\n<span class=SpellE>am&#259;nun&#355;it</span>. Modalitatea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nprocedura de raportare a auditorilor interni se stabilesc potrivit normelor\nelaborate de Camera Auditorilor Financiari din România.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Adunarea general&#259; poate\naproba <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span> financiare anuale numai\ndac&#259; acestea sunt <span class=SpellE>înso&#355;ite</span> de raportul\ncenzorilor sau, dup&#259; caz, al auditorilor financiari.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>[textul din Art. 163, alin. (4) din\ntitlul III, capitolul IV, <span class=SpellE>sectiunea</span> IV a fost abrogat\nla 01-dec-2006 de </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Art. I, punctul 119. din <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> 441/2006</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>]</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1423283841\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1999\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1423283841\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Cenzorii sau, dup&#259; caz, auditorii interni vor aduce\nla <span class=SpellE>cuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259;</span> membrilor consiliului de\n<span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> neregulile în <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> înc&#259;lc&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nlegale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> ale prevederilor actului constitutiv\npe care le constata, iar cazurile mai importante le vor aduce la <span\nclass=SpellE>cuno&#351;tin&#355;&#259;</span> adun&#259;rii generale.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}